# AI Chat 补充规则
# ACL4SSR 已覆盖: OpenAI, Claude, Gemini, Grok(x.ai), Meta AI,
#   Perplexity, Mistral, Copilot, Cursor, Sydney/Bing
# 以下为 ACL4SSR 未覆盖的 AI 服务

# Grok AI (xai.com not covered by upstream x.ai)
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,xai.com

# Microsoft AI (extras not in upstream)
DOMAIN,designer.microsoft.com
DOMAIN,www.bingapis.com
DOMAIN,edgeservices.bing.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,ai.microsoft.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,studio.microsoft.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,azure.ai

# Groq (upstream only has DOMAIN for api/console, not DOMAIN-SUFFIX)
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,groq.com

# Cohere
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,cohere.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,coral.cohere.com

# OpenRouter (AI model aggregator)
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,openrouter.ai

# Meta AI (llama subdomain not in upstream)
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,llama.meta.com